SELECT 75, Farm_ID FROM competition_record INNER JOIN farm_competition ON farm_competition.Competition_ID = competition_record.Competition_ID WHERE ( competition_record.Competition_ID >= RAND(88 - 3)) AND (Hosts NOT IN (SELECT Hosts FROM farm_competition WHERE Theme NOT IN ALL (SELECT Theme FROM farm_competition AS s WHERE (s.Competition_ID IN (1, 2, 3, 40, 5)) OR (s.Theme NOT LIKE %[^xyz]%)) LIMIT 8)) GROUP BY Farm_ID HAVING MAX(farm_competition.Competition_ID) = 26 ORDER BY 75 ASC LIMIT 4 OFFSET 2
